# Data Dictionary — obadage2024_citations_repro

## Data source
ML Reproducibility Challenge 2022 papers + 41,244 citation contexts (Semantic Scholar) — ML papers + citation contexts for reproducibility prediction
Access: public; Provenance: Zenodo 10.5281/zenodo.10895748; GitHub lamps-lab/ccair-ai-reproducibility

## Key variables
- Unit of analysis: citation context
- Time window: MLRC 2022
- Sample N: 41244
- Filter rules: citation-context extraction via Semantic Scholar Graph API

## Indicator definitions
- Formula: Citation-context features → reproducibility score (M1-M7 models)
- Parameters: sentiment features, 5-fold CV
- Computation steps: extract citation contexts, compute sentiment features, train M1-M7
